python binding to plyflatten installable via "pip install plyflatten"

To update the pypi hub, you need an account on pypi, and then run the following
commands:

        # update version number on file plyflatten/__about__.py
	python setup.py sdist bdist_wheel
	python -m twine upload dist/plyflatten-X.tar.gz
	rm -rf build dist plyflatten.egg-info
